			<h3></h3>
		I slightly disagree with Wxmang this time. First, as someone already said, the amount of money obtained by Li Zhicheng is questionable. Second, the whole system of Ming dynasty is corrupted. Chongzheng's own ability is not a critical issue in this big background. People are laughing at Chongzhen nowadays. However if you were at that place at that time, would you be better than him? I doubt it. We feel that Chongzheng is terrible because we already know many facts which are clear after several hundred years. However several hundred years ago, things are not clear at all.<br />
